{
  "video_id": "5ODzO7Lz_pw",
  "title": "Thomas Thwaites: How I built a toaster -- from scratch",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "If we look around us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "much of what surrounds us"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "started life as various rocks and sludge"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "buried in the ground in various places in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "But, of course, they don&#39;t look like rocks and sludge now."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "They look like TV cameras, monitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "annoying radio mics."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "And so this magical transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "is what I was trying to get at with my project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "which became known as the Toaster Project."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "And it was also inspired by this quote"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "from Douglas Adams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "and the situation is from \"The Hitchhiker&#39;s Guide to the Galaxy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "And the situation it describes"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "is the hero of the book -- he&#39;s a 20th-century man --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "finds himself alone on a strange planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "populated only by a technologically primitive people."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "And he kind of assumes that, yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "he&#39;ll become -- these villagers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "he&#39;ll become their emperor"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "and transform their society"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "with his wonderful command of technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "and science and the elements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "but, of course, realizes"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "that without the rest of human society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "he can barely make a sandwich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "let alone a toaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "But he didn&#39;t have Wikipedia."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "So I thought, okay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll try and make an electric toaster from scratch."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "And, working on the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "that the cheapest electric toaster"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "would also be the simplest to reverse-engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "I went and bought the cheapest toaster I could find,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "took it home"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "and was kind of dismayed to discover"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "that, inside this object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "which I&#39;d bought for just 3.49 pounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "there were 400 different bits"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "made out of a hundred-plus different materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t have the rest of my life to do this project."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "I had maybe nine months."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "So I thought, okay, I&#39;ll start with five."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "And these were steel, mica,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "plastic, copper and nickel."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "So, starting with steel: how do you make steel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "I went and knocked on the door"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "of the Rio Tinto Chair"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "of Advanced Mineral Extraction at the Royal School of Mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "and said, \"How do you make steel?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "And Professor Cilliers was very kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "and talked me through it."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "And my vague rememberings from GCSE science --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "well, steel comes from iron,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "so I phoned up an iron mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "And said, \"Hi, I&#39;m trying to make a toaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "Can I come up and get some iron?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, when I got there -- emerges Ray."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "He had misheard me"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "and thought I was coming up because I was trying to make a poster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "and so wasn&#39;t prepared to take me into the mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "But after some nagging, I got him to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "(Video) Ray: It was Crease Limestone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "and that was produced"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "by sea creatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "350 million years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "in a nice, warm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "sunny atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "When you study geology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "you can see what&#39;s happened in the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "and there were terrific changes in the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "Thomas Thwaites: As you can see, they had the Christmas decorations up."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "And of course, it wasn&#39;t actually a working mine anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "because, though Ray was a miner there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "the mine had closed"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "and had been reopened as a kind of tourist attraction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "because, of course, it can&#39;t compete"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "on the scale of operations which are happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "in South America, Australia, wherever."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "But anyway, I got my suitcase of iron ore"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "and dragged it back to London on the train,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "and then was faced with the problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "Okay, how do you make this rock"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "into components for a toaster?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "So I went back to Professor Cilliers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"Go to the library.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "So I did"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "and was looking through the undergraduate textbooks on metallurgy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "completely useless for what I was trying to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "Because, of course, they don&#39;t actually tell you how to do it"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "if you want to do it yourself and you don&#39;t have a smelting plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "So I ended up going to the History of Science Library"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "and looking at this book."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "This is the first textbook on metallurgy"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "written in the West, at least."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "And there you can see that woodcut"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "is basically what I ended up doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 263260.0,
      "text": "But instead of a bellows, I had a leaf blower."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 263260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "And that was something that reoccurred throughout the project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "was, the smaller the scale you want to work on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "the further back in time you have to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "And so this is after"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "a day and about half a night"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "smelting this iron."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "I dragged out this stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "and it wasn&#39;t iron."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "But luckily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "I found a patent online"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "for industrial furnaces that use microwaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "and at 30 minutes at full power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "and I was able to finish off the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "So, my next --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 306260.0,
      "text": "The next thing I was trying to get was copper."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 306260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "Again, this mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "was once the largest copper mine in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "but I found a retired geology professor"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "to take me down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"Okay, I&#39;ll let you have some water from the mine.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "And the reason I was interested in getting water"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "is because water which goes through mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "becomes kind of acidic"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "and will start picking up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "dissolving the minerals from the mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "And a good example of this is the Rio Tinto,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "which is in Portugal."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "As you can see, it&#39;s got lots and lots of minerals dissolved in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "So many such"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s now just a home for bacteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "who really like acidic, toxic conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "But anyway, the water I dragged back"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "from the Isle of Anglesey where the mine was --"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "there was enough copper in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "such that I could cast the pins"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "of my metal electric plug."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "So my next thing: I was off to Scotland"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "to get mica."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "And mica is a mineral"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "which is a very good insulator"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "and very good at insulating electricity."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s me getting mica."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "And the last material I&#39;m going to talk about today is plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "and, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "my toaster had to have a plastic case."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "Plastic is the defining feature"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 386260.0,
      "text": "of cheap electrical goods."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "And so plastic comes from oil, so I phoned up BP"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "and spent a good half an hour"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "trying to convince the PR office at BP"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "that it would be fantastic for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "if they flew me to an oil rig"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 399260.0,
      "text": "and let me have a jug of oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 399260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "BP obviously has a bit more on their mind now."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "But even then"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "they weren&#39;t convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "and said, \"Okay, we&#39;ll phone you back\" -- never did."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "So I looked at other ways of making plastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "And you can actually make plastic"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "from obviously oils which come from plants, but also from starches."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "So this is attempting to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "potato starch plastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "And for a while that was looking really good."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "I poured it into the mold, which you can see there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "which I&#39;ve made from a tree trunk."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "And it was looking good for a while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "but I left it outside, because you had to leave it outside to dry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 435260.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately I came back"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "and there were snails eating the unhydrolyzed bits of potato."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "So kind of out of desperation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "I decided that I could think laterally."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 447260.0,
      "text": "And geologists have actually christened --"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 449260.0,
      "text": "well, they&#39;re debating whether to christen --"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 449260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "the age that we&#39;re living in --"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re debating whether to make it a new geological epoch"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "called the Anthropocene, the age of Man."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because geologists of the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "would kind of see a sharp shift"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "in the strata of rock that is being laid down now."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "So suddenly, it will become kind of radioactive from Chernobyl"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "and the 2,000 or so nuclear bombs"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 468260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "that have been set off since 1945."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 472260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;d also be an extinction event --"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "like fossils would suddenly disappear."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "And also, I thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 482260.0,
      "text": "that there would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 484260.0,
      "text": "synthetic polymers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 484260.0,
      "end_time": 486260.0,
      "text": "plastics, embedded in the rock."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 488260.0,
      "text": "So I looked up a plastic --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 488260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "so I decided that I could mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 492260.0,
      "text": "some of this modern-day rock."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 494260.0,
      "text": "And I went up to Manchester"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 494260.0,
      "end_time": 497260.0,
      "text": "to visit a place called Axion Recycling."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 497260.0,
      "end_time": 500260.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re at the sharp end of what&#39;s called the WEEE,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 500260.0,
      "end_time": 504260.0,
      "text": "which is this European electrical and electronic waste directive."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "And that was brought into force"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 510260.0,
      "text": "to try and deal with the mountain of stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 510260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "that is just being made"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "and then living for a while in our homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "and then going to landfill."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "But this is it."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 526260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 591260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "of my toaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 597260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it without the case on."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 603260.0,
      "text": "And there it is on the shelves."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 605260.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 609260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 609260.0,
      "end_time": 611260.0,
      "text": "Bruno Giussani: I&#39;m told you did plug it in once."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 611260.0,
      "end_time": 613260.0,
      "text": "TT: Yeah, I did plug it in."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 613260.0,
      "end_time": 615260.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if you could see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 615260.0,
      "end_time": 618260.0,
      "text": "but I was never able to make insulation for the wires."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 618260.0,
      "end_time": 620260.0,
      "text": "Kew Gardens were insistent"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 620260.0,
      "end_time": 623260.0,
      "text": "that I couldn&#39;t come and hack into their rubber tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 623260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "So the wires were uninsulated."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 627260.0,
      "text": "So there was 240 volts"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 627260.0,
      "end_time": 629260.0,
      "text": "going through these homemade copper wires,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 629260.0,
      "end_time": 631260.0,
      "text": "homemade plug."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 631260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "And for about five seconds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "the toaster toasted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 637260.0,
      "text": "but then, unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 637260.0,
      "end_time": 640260.0,
      "text": "the element kind of melted itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 640260.0,
      "end_time": 643260.0,
      "text": "But I considered it a partial success, to be honest."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 643260.0,
      "end_time": 646260.0,
      "text": "BG: Thomas Thwaites. TT: Thanks."
    }
  ]
}